    "dynamic_line": "&The scientist looks shocked to see you, and quickly tucks a large object under their lab coat.  They then address you with a quivering, yet indignant tone.  \"Wh-who are you?  How did you get in here?  D-don't know who I am?!  Leave, or I'll have y-y-you killed!\"",
